{"tid":1511889,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"預防白色恐怖／清算，做個精明網絡用家","createTime":"2019-08-27T16:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T03:05:07.000Z","uid":23094,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a9e7c5f4d84c7e13eeff1b16c94600eb1d76d582","tid":1511889,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"等我呢隻IT9小薯教大家做好基本網絡安全措施<br />\n保障自己嘅網絡私隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日同大家講下DNS（Domain Name Server）<br />\nDNS就好似一個電話簿咁<br />\n入面有好多電話號碼（IP address／網絡協定地址）<br />\n每個電話號碼都對應住一個名（Domain name／網絡域名）<br />\n<br />\n你好難記得咁多電話號碼，但係名就易記好多<br />\n當你想打某個電話號碼嗰陣，你會揀返嗰個名<br />\n咁個電話簿就幫你揾下個名對應住嘅電話號碼係幾多<br />\n然後講返個電話號碼畀你知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點就喺呢度<br />\n1. 究竟係邊個提供呢本電話簿畀你？<br />\n2. 提供電話簿畀嗰個人咪知道哂你打過去邊？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 通常係電訊／網絡供應商（ISP／Internet Service Provider）<br />\n如果你申請咗電訊／網絡服務之後冇做過任何設定<br />\n咁預設DNS就通常係由ISP提供<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而你其實可以選擇改用其他可信／更安全／更快速嘅DNS<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 係<br />\nDNS絕對有能力知道你上過咩網<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如你喺邊段時間曾經上過連登、YouTube、PornHub⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢只係唔知道你喺嗰啲網站入面嘅實際活動<br />\n但係其實知道你喺咩時間上過咩網已經足夠令Popo得到好多資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔知道你嘅ISP幾時會出賣你啲資料畀Popo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要保障自己唔畀ISP知道自己上過咩網<br />\n最好嘅方法就係用自己信得過嘅DNS<br />\n1.1.1.1 就係其中一個安全／可靠／快速／保障私隱嘅DNS<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhttps://1.1.1.1/dns/<br />\n<br />\n1.1.1.1係由Cloudflare提供<br />\nCloudflare係一間咩公司，可信度有幾高，應該唔難Google<br />\n連登都係用佢哋做網絡安全方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.1.1.1標榜「私隱為先」，唔會記錄任何IP<br />\n而且1.1.1.1比起一般ISP或者Google提供嘅DNS都快好撚多<br />\n唔好睇少嗰幾十ms，100個幾十ms就係幾秒<br />\n喺緊要關頭遲幾秒接收資訊就足以影響你一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面條Link入面已經有哂唔同裝置嘅設定教學<br />\n如果係iOS／Android仲簡單<br />\nDownload個App撳個掣就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">做個精明網民</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S.<br />\n換DNS並唔代表可以隱藏IP address<br />\n你上過嘅網站仍然有可能會記錄低你嘅IP address<br />\n然後揾機會將你出賣畀Popo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be061484ff480e7174ce123580961c54b2b8763b","tid":1511889,"uid":55128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/suRKmvs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRKmvs.gif&h=09fb3e14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxs0BU04RHr%2BP31d0xuhNw0M%3D&h=08648028\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxs0BU04RHr%2BP31d0xuhNw0M%3D&h=6164d584\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupr